The Manchurian Candidate;;63;;80;;R;;Years after his squad was ambushed during the Gulf War, Major Ben Marco (Denzel Washington) finds himself having terrible nightmares. He begins to doubt that his fellow squad-mate Sergeant Raymond Shaw (Liev Schreiber), now a vice-presidential candidate, is the hero he remembers him being. As Marco's doubts deepen, Shaw's political power grows, and, when Marco finds a mysterious implant embedded in his back, the memory of what really happened begins to return.;;Drama,Mystery & thriller;;Jonathan Demme;;2004;;Denzel Washington,Meryl Streep,Liev Schreiber,Jon Voight,Kimberly Elise,Jeffrey Wright,Ted Levine,Bruno Ganz,Miguel Ferrer,Dean Stockwell,Jude Ciccolella,Simon McBurney,Vera Farmiga,Obba Babatunde,Zeljko Ivanek,Paul Lazar,John Bedford Lloyd,Anthony Mackie,Tom Stechschulte,Robyn Hitchcock;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/manchurian_candidate